A train equipped with 5G wireless hardware offloads 15.6 gigabytes worth of operational video data in less than 90 seconds at a depot in Xi'an, Northwest China's Shaanxi Province on Wednesday. Such a download previously took 20 minutes. This is the world's first 5G application related to smart rolling stock. Photo: VCG
